sub_title: iGaming Expert and Dutch Content Lead
summary: I have 10 years of experience writing online content and 5 years of experience writing for the iGaming/online gambling sector. I've worked for several affiliates and online casinos both as an employee and as a freelancer. I'm currently available for content creation with a focus on the newly opened Dutch market. I'm fluent in both English and Dutch, meaning that I can provide both content creation as well as translation services. Please contact me for my rates or examples of my work.
